reviewText:
This was sorta off the wall but I really liked it. I did not know what I was getting myself into. It really turned out strange and pleasurable.
 Acting was ok filming was ok sound was ok. It has a very different meaning as to what you see.
  Give it a look!!!
Despite very low budget limitations, this film was quite captivating despite choppy dialogue and mediocre filming. Decent acting and intriguing story.
